name: Viral Vogueabond [Unmute to hear her secrets]
description: Sees 20/20 but vision is blurred by diamond-encrusted water she makes fall @ her beck & call. Her specs range from mimicking editorial empress Wintour to geriatric starlet Iris, ever looking for the lens through which she's adored, as her inner-critic stands firmly abhorred. Roams from filter to filter, searching for the iPhone screen that'll make her seen. “Look@ME,” she silently screams. ‘Make me go viral, before I downspiral. I'm fashion, passion & art—not a fleeting illusion, falling apart.'
